        "1d899558-ffdf-49ba-9334-d43a3e92b84e": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>If you are not completely satisfied with an EDWIN USA purchase or gift for any reason, we gladly accept returns of merchandise for a full refund if we receive your return within 30 days of the date of purchase. If not returned or shipped to return within the 30 days since you received your purchase, unfortunately we can’t offer you a refund or exchange.</p><p>To initiate a return, access the order details on your Order Confirmation email. If you have any issues locating your Order Confirmation email, please feel free to contact us  for assistance in processing your return request - Contact@edwin-usa.com.</p><p>Once we receive the goods we will issue you a return. Refunds may take up to 3-7 business days to process from the date of merchandise receipt in our warehouse.</p><p>Please review our return, refund and exchange policies for edwin-usa.com purchases below. Merchandise must be returned in unworn, unused, and undamaged condition with all original tags attached. Please note that all returns are subject to validation and approval at Edwin’s discretion.</p><p></p><p>As of December 9th, 2024, all Sale items are final sale and cannot be returned for a refund or exchanged for another item. In the event you need to exchange your item for a different size, we can facilitate a same-style exchange pending stock availability. Please reach out to our Customer Care Team to help you with your exchange request - Contact@edwin-usa.com. </p>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
