            "heading": "Return Process Instructions",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>To initiate a return, access the order details on your Order Confirmation email. If you have any issues locating your Order Confirmation email, please feel free to contact us  for assistance in processing your return request - Contact@edwin-usa.com.</p><p>Within 48 hours, you will receive an emailed prepaid return label (pre-paid label is sent by email only and not mailed out; label will be voided after 14 days). Please ensure the item(s) in original condition are packaged properly and affix the prepaid label to the outside of your package, make a note of the tracking number, and leave the package with chosen shipping courier (UPS or Fedex). Shipping charges are prepaid by Edwin-usa and no additional postage is required. </p><p>Please allow 5-7 days for processing. Additional delays may occur.</p><p> </p><p>*If you’ve submitted a return and have not received a slip within 72 hours, please check your email spam/junk folder as your return slip may have been sent here. We apologize for any inconvenience and can provide further assistance from our Customer Care Team at <a href=\"mailto:contact@edwin-usa.com\">contact@edwin-usa.com</a></p>",
